Onboarding.WhatIsOONIProbe.Title: Ce este OONI Probe?
Onboarding.WhatIsOONIProbe.Paragraph:
Aplicația dvs. pentru măsurarea cenzurii pe internet.

Site-urile web și aplicațiile de social media sunt blocate? Conexiunea dvs. de internet este neobișnuit de lentă?

Rulați OONI Probe pentru a afla de ce!
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Title: Atenție!
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.1: Datele OONI sunt publicate în mod deschis și vor include informații despre rețeaua dvs.
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.2: Oricine vă monitorizează activitatea pe internet (de exemplu, guvern sau ISP) va vedea că executați OONI Probe.
Onboarding.ThingsToKnow.Bullet.3: Puteți testa site-urile web interzise (dar puteți alege care sunt site-urile de testat).
Onboarding.PopQuiz.Title: Test rapid
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Title: Întrebarea 1/2
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Question: Dacă cineva îmi monitorizează activitatea pe internet, va vedea că eu rulez OONI Probe.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Wrong.Title: Avertizare
Onboarding.PopQuiz.1.Wrong.Paragraph: OONI Probe nu este un instrument de confidențialitate. Oricine vă monitorizează activitatea pe internet va vedea ce software executați.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Title: Întrebarea 2/2
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Question: De fiecare dată când rulez OONI Probe, datele rețelei pe care le colectez vor fi publicate automat.
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Wrong.Title: Avertizare
Onboarding.PopQuiz.2.Wrong.Paragraph: Pentru a crește transparența cenzurii pe internet, datele din rețea ale tuturor utilizatorilor OONI Probe sunt publicate automat (cu excepția cazului în care acestea sunt dezactivate în setări).
Onboarding.AutomatedTesting.Title: Automated testing
Onboarding.AutomatedTesting.Paragraph:
To measure internet censorship every day, please enable automated testing so that OONI Probe can run tests periodically.

Don't worry, we'll be mindful of battery usage. 

You can disable automated testing from the settings at any time.
Onboarding.Crash.Title: Crash Reporting
Onboarding.Crash.Paragraph:
To improve OONI Probe we would like to collect anonymous crash reports when the app does not work properly.

Would you like to opt-in to submitting crash reports to the OONI development team?
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Title: Setări implicite
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Bullet.1: Codul țării (de exemplu IT pentru Italia)
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Bullet.2: Informații despre rețea (inclusiv numărul de sistem autonom - ASN)
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Paragraph:
We do our best not to publish your IP address or any other potentially personally identifiable information.

Learn more through [OONI's Data Policy](https://ooni.org/about/data-policy/).
Onboarding.DefaultSettings.Paragraph.1: By tapping "OK", you will share crash reports to help us improve OONI Probe.

Dashboard.Card.Subtitle: Atingeți cardul pentru detalii
Dashboard.Websites.Overview.Paragraph:
Check whether websites are blocked using OONI's [Web Connectivity test](https://ooni.org/nettest/web-connectivity/).

Every time you tap Run, you test different websites from the Citizen Lab's [global](https://github.com/citizenlab/test-lists/blob/master/lists/global.csv) and [country-specific](https://github.com/citizenlab/test-lists/tree/master/lists) test lists.

To test the sites of your choice, tap the Choose websites button or select categories of sites via the settings of this card. 

This test measures whether websites are blocked by means of DNS tampering, TCP/IP blocking or by a transparent HTTP proxy.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.Websites.Overview.Paragraph.De:
Check whether websites are blocked using OONI's [Web Connectivity test](https://ooni.org/nettest/web-connectivity/).

You will test the websites included in the Citizen Lab's [global](https://github.com/citizenlab/test-lists/blob/master/lists/global.csv) and [country-specific](https://github.com/citizenlab/test-lists/tree/master/lists) test lists.

This test measures whether websites are blocked by means of DNS tampering, TCP/IP blocking or by a transparent HTTP proxy.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.Performance.Overview.Paragraph:
Measure the speed and performance of your network using the [NDT](https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/) test.

Measure video streaming performance using the [DASH](https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/) test.

These tests consume data depending on your network speed.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).

Disclaimer: These tests rely on third party servers. We therefore cannot guarantee that your IP address will not be collected.

Prin rularea testelor din acest card, veți:

- măsura viteza și performanța rețelei (testul [NDT](https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/))
- măsura performanța pentru streaming video (testul [DASH](https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/))
- verifica prezența [tehnologiilor middlebox](https://ooni.org/support/glossary/#middlebox) din rețeaua dvs. (testele [HTTP Invalid Request Line](https://ooni.org/nettest/http-invalid-request-line/) și [HTTP Header Field Manipulation](https://ooni.org/nettest/http-header-field-manipulation/))

Aceste teste consumă date în funcție de viteza rețelei.

Rezultatele testului dvs. vor fi publicate pe [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/) și [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).

**Disclaimer:** Testele [NDT](https://ooni.org/nettest/ndt/) și [DASH](https://ooni.org/nettest/dash/) sunt efectuate pe servere terțe furnizate de [Measurement Lab (M-Lab)](https://www.measurementlab.net/). Dacă efectuați aceste teste, M-Lab va colecta și publica adresa dvs. IP (în scopuri de cercetare), indiferent de setările dvs. OONI Sonda. Aflați mai multe despre guvernanța datelor M-Lab prin intermediul [declarației de confidențialitate](https://www.measurementlab.net/privacy/).
Dashboard.Middleboxes.Overview.Paragraph:
Internet Service Providers often use network appliances (middleboxes) for various networking purposes (such as caching). Sometimes these middleboxes are used to implement internet censorship and/or surveillance.

Find middleboxes in your network using OONI's [HTTP Invalid Request Line](https://ooni.org/nettest/http-invalid-request-line/) and [HTTP Header Field Manipulation](https://ooni.org/nettest/http-header-field-manipulation/) tests.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.InstantMessaging.Card.Descript: Testarea blocării aplicațiilor de mesagerie instantanee
Dashboard.InstantMessaging.Overview.Para:
Check whether [WhatsApp](https://ooni.org/nettest/whatsapp/), [Facebook Messenger](https://ooni.org/nettest/facebook-messenger/), [Telegram](https://ooni.org/nettest/telegram/), and [Signal](https://ooni.org/nettest/signal) are blocked.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/world/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).
Dashboard.Circumvention.Card.Description: Testarea blocării instrumentelor de eludare a cenzurii
Dashboard.Circumvention.Overview.Paragra:
Check whether [Psiphon](https://ooni.org/nettest/psiphon/), [Tor](https://ooni.org/nettest/tor/) or [RiseupVPN](https://ooni.org/nettest/riseupvpn/) are blocked.

Your results will be published on [OONI Explorer](https://explorer.ooni.org/) and [OONI API](https://api.ooni.io/).

Settings.About.Label: Despre OONI
Settings.About.Content.Paragraph:
Open Observatory of Network Interference (OONI) este un program gratuit este un proiect de software gratuit din Tor Project care are drept scop creșterea transparenței cenzurii pe internetul din întreaga lume.

Din 2012, comunitatea globală OONI a măsurat rețelele din peste 200 de țări. Unele dintre aceste măsurători servesc drept dovadă a cenzurii pe internet.
Settings.Notifications.Label: Notificări
Settings.AutomatedTesting.Label: Automated testing
Settings.AutomatedTesting.RunAutomatical:
By enabling automatic testing, OONI Probe tests will run automatically multiple times per day. Your test results will automatically get published on OONI Explorer: https://explorer.ooni.org/ 

Important: If you have a VPN enabled, OONI Probe will not run tests automatically. Please turn off your VPN for automated OONI Probe testing. Learn more: https://ooni.org/support/faq/#can-i-run-ooni-probe-over-a-vpn
Settings.Sharing.Label: Partajare
Settings.Sharing.IncludeCountryCode.PopU: Aceste informații (de exemplu, IT pentru Italia) sunt necesare pentru a identifica din ce țară sunt colectate măsurătorile. Sigur doriți să dezactivați această opțiune?
Settings.Sharing.Footer:
Prin publicarea rezultatelor, sporiți transparența interferenței rețelei și sprijiniți comunitatea OONI. 

Informațiile de rețea (adică numărul de sistem autonom) sunt necesare pentru identificarea furnizorilor de servicii Internet.
